import { BrowserRouter,Routes,Route } from "react-router-dom"
import Home from "../views/Home"

const Rutas = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
      <Route index element={<Layout/>}> 
   <Route index element={<Home/>} />

   </Route>
    </Routes>
    
    </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  )
}

export default Rutas
